| ''getVariantTemplates($variant)'' | ''2026-03-11'' | Returns the configured filename templates for ''big'' or ''small''. |
| ''normalizeIconBaseName($name)'' | ''2026-03-11'' | Normalizes an icon filename without namespace or extension. |
