===== Event =====

On upload or deletion, the plugin emits:
  * ''PLUGIN_PAGESICON_UPDATED''

Payload:
  * ''target_page''
  * ''action''
  * ''media_id''

Consumer plugins remain responsible for their own cache invalidation.

